NOTE ON VOICE SAMPLES AND QUOTATIONS

Persona files in this repository contain verbatim excerpts (300–500 words each)
from copyrighted books, articles, talks, and podcasts authored by the named
experts. These excerpts are used for transformative skill construction —
teaching the Claude AI assistant to imitate each expert's voice and frameworks
when producing original responses.

The MIT license above applies to the skill structure, routing logic, schema,
and original commentary in this repository. It does NOT grant rights to the
underlying copyrighted source material excerpted within. If you are reusing
voice samples or direct quotations outside the scope of this skill (for
example, republishing them as standalone content), you must obtain
permission from the original rights holders.

Source attributions are listed in ATTRIBUTIONS.md and per-persona MANIFEST.md
files.
